These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, magic-tricks, puzzles
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, canasta, poker
House: tower, ranch-style, palace, farmhouse
There 4 different types of food: potato, pomegranate, tomato, lettuce
1. the ranch-style house is the person playing poker##1
2. the palace house is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
3. the ranch-style house is the person eating potato##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating potato##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the tower house##1
6. the person eating tomato is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
7. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
8. the tower house is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | traveling | puzzles   | collecting  | magic-tricks  |
| Game   | monopoly    | poker    | mah-jongg      | canasta    |
| House   | farmhouse | ranch-style | palace | tower |
| Food     | lettuce  | potato       | pomegranate    | tomato     |

