.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, poppy, lily
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, pop, punk, indie
City: liverpool, colone, paris, san-francisco
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, montecristo, blend, swisher
1. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
5. the fan indie is between the person traveling to paris and the alhambra-smoker##2
6. the swisher-smoker is between the fan indie and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
8. the fan pop is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
9. the fan punk is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Flower         | lily | tulip    | poppy  | rose    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | pop  | indie  | punk |
| City           | san-francisco      | paris       | colone      | liverpool       |
| Cigar         | montecristo    | swisher | blend | alhambra |

