3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the pakistani##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is the mexican##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the pakistani##1
8. the person who's sport is cycling is between the thai and the mexican##2
9. the pakistani is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person watching zombie movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Sport        | rowing | surfing     | cycling   | badminton     |
| Nationality       | german   | thai   | pakistani | mexican |
| Movie-Genre         | drama   | satire | spy       | zombie    |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | bird | rat  | mouse    |

